        <mxCell id="BocphrOwTB-a-wmXy_JW-1" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;" value="Virtual Envoirnment&lt;div&gt;- isolated workspace just like container&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- eases up the project setup&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- solves the configuration issues, make dependencies local for a specific project&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- helps in team collaboration as well&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼs&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Desktop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼs&quot;&gt;mkdir&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;ai-hackathon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼs&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;ai-hackathon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;python&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼn&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;m&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;venv&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;venv&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;This Creates:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;ai-hackathon/&lt;br&gt;├── venv/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Activate the vartiual env:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;venv&lt;/span&gt;\&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&quot;&gt;Scripts&lt;/span&gt;\&lt;span class=&quot;ͼt&q